  • Classes in it.polimi.ingsw.ps42.model.position used by it.polimi.ingsw.ps42.model 
    Class and Description
    CouncilPosition
    Implementation of the Council position, the table will have an arrayList of this class.
    MarketPosition
    Implementation of the Market position, gives to the player a certain amount of resources or a council privilege
    TowerPosition
    Implementation for the tower position, has a card that have to be setted in every round.
    YieldAndProductPosition
    Implementation for both the Yield and Product position since they do the same job but on different type of cards: they allow the player to do a Yield/Product action
